{
  "----*Actors 2020_08_05 20:19*----": "----*Actors 2020_08_05 20:19*----",
  "Eric": "埃里克",
  "Silver Reaper": "银之死神",
  "A veteran warrior who fought on many battlefields.\r\nHe becomes uncontrollable in battle when berserk.": "历经数次战场洗礼的雇佣兵。虽然平时很温和，\r\n但是一进入战斗就会化身为狂战士。",
  "Natalie": "娜塔丽",
  "Thunder Fist": "赤色闪电",
  "Her father is a master assassin. Throughout her\r\nyouth, she mastered the techniques of fighting.": "其祖父是使用爪的高手，因此在年幼时她就学会\r\n了无数格斗技巧。",
  "Terence": "泰伦斯",
  "Wandering Paladin": "流浪骑士",
  "Stripped of his status. He wanders around protecting\r\nothers and stays true to his code of honour.": "因被人暗算失去了圣骑士地位，但如今依然为了\r\n骑士精神而四处修行。",
  "Ernest": "阿奈思特",
  "Magic Swordsman": "魔剑继承者",
  "A wandering swordsman looking for his master.\r\nHe is one who has mastered the Magic Sword.": "为了替师傅报仇而踏上旅途，\r\n能够把魔法的力量寄宿在剑刃之中。",
  "Ryoma": "龙马",
  "Dawn's Edge": "晓之钢剑",
  "He is the current owner of Takeshi's blade. His\r\nmovements are fluid and sharp like a knife.": "在东瀛有着“无双之钢剑”称号的樱花一刀流\r\n剑士，一闪而过的刀锋沉重而锋利。",
  "Brenda": "布伦达",
  "Dark Green Aim": "森林守护者",
  "A girl who's brought up by forest spirits. She loves\r\nnature and protects the forest from disturbance.": "精灵之森养育的少女，热爱自然，不允许任何人\r\n扰乱森林的宁静，也有些向往都市生活。",
  "Rick": "瑞克",
  "Formless Wind": "无影疾风",
  "His youth is bound by hatred. He acts like a \r\nwise-crack due to his life.": "自称讨厌被约束的义贼青年，非常多嘴，\r\n是一个愿意为朋友献出生命的热血男儿。",
  "Alice": "爱丽丝",
  "Saviour of Joan": "救世圣女",
  "A woman whose destiny was to become a saint. She\r\nis full of passion and gives equal love to the enemy.": "根据神谕有着圣女使命的女子，充满同情心的她\r\n即便是敌人也会给予相同的爱。",
  "Isabelle": "伊萨贝拉",
  "Graceful Nightmare": "优雅的恶梦",
  "A witch who delivered fear to mankind. But through a\r\nfailed reincarnation, she has lost her memory.": "一直带给人类恐惧的魔女，转生术失败后，失去\r\n了大部分的记忆，但却流露出原来善良的本性。",
  "Noah": "诺亚",
  "Star Seer": "观星者",
  "A hermit who avoids the populace by living in the\r\nmountains. He seeks the true identity of the evil star.": "为避世俗而隐居在山林中的贤者，为寻找凶星的\r\n真实身份而踏上寻找“最遥远之书库”的旅途。",
